### Debug JWT Token

### 1. Đăng ký user mới trước
POST http://localhost:5016/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "birthday": "2000-01-01",
  "gender": "Nam",
  "location": "Hà Nội"
}

### 2. Đăng nhập với user mới
POST http://localhost:5016/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Đăng nhập với user cũ (nếu cần)
POST http://localhost:5016/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "H@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Test với token từ bước 1 (thay YOUR_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:5016/api/movies/1/Comments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### 3. Test gửi bình luận với token (thay YOUR_TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:5016/api/movies/1/Comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "text": "Test comment"
}

### 4. Test không có token (sẽ lỗi 401)
POST http://localhost:5016/api/movies/1/Comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Test comment without token"
}
